description: Outlets to Go™ 3 USB Worldwide: Your Must-Have Worldwide Travel CompanionWhether you’re traveling across town, or to the other side of the world, there’s nothing worse than getting to your hotel or meeting room and not having enough power outlets for all your electronics. Outlets to Go 3 USB Worldwide easily fits in a small bag or laptop case and the included adapter lets you plug in virtually anywhere in the world. Wherever you go, keep all your electronics powered up with Outlets to Go.Extra Outlets and USB Charging Wherever You Need ThemWith Outlets to Go 3 USB you've got the extra outlets you need when you're traveling plus a rapid-charging high-power USB port to charge your portable devices like cell phones, cameras, and more.Lots of Convenient Features in a Small PackageFor added convenience, wide-spaced outlets let you plug in bulky power adapters without blocking other outlets and Monster's Flatwrap™ cord management system makes it easy to pack away the cord to eliminate clutter. The FlatProfile™ plug is designed to fit behind furniture in even the tightest spaces.
title: Monster Outlets To Go MP OTG300 LTOP 300 for Laptops 3 Outlets, 2 USB - Bubble Package
